      <Quotations id="ritualQuotations">
         <ab><ab>Revāyat of Behdin Ǧāsā (MU1, p. I. 593), on the Nērang ī Āb ud Padyāb ceremony:</ab>
            <ab class="ab_indent">barsam avar māhruy nahādan zud bāyad ke naǧonbide (AVPerTr.) <em>ḫešnus̱ar ahurahi mazdā</em> (Per.) tā  (AvPerTr.)<em>setumi</em></ab>
            <ab class="ab_indent">The <em>barsom</em> has to be placed on the <em>māhrūy</em>. The <em>zōt</em> should not stir. (They should recite) <em>xšnaōϑra ahurahe mazdā̊</em> until <em>staōmi</em>.</ab></ab>
      </Quotations>
   </Ritual>
